project: SYSTEM: Welcome!  Are you playing with a touch screen or on a computer?

Collect the green squares and avoid red wquares.  If you're playing on computer the player will follow your mouse.  If you're playing with touch, drag the player (note: touch is a little glitchy).  Score at least 130 to earn tokens.  You can earn additional tokens at different points over 130.  Good luck!

On computer the player (bottom square) will follow your mouse.  On touch screen the player will follow your finger (drag it).  You will start to fall.  Touch the falling blocks to keep your position in the air.  Get the highest score possible.  The background might be a little glitchy on black and white mode, sorry.  Good luck!
Note: You can only earn whole tokens, and they're rounded down to whole numbers, so you may not notice your multiplier working every time.  Multiplier does NOT apply the the mystery prize
